title: Arbor Skateboards :: Product Profiles - Mindstate
description:
The Mindstate mixes the classic styling of a pintail with the performance of a drop-through and a fiberglass-reinforced flex. Count on a smooth, responsive ride and an easy push and turn.
Artist: Matt Smith

L: 37.50” W: 8.75” WB: 27.50”
To learn more about the Mindstate visit: arborcollective.com/skateboards/products/mindstate-walnut/
